Span.Text: Enable rapid decision making and mitigate threats with improved data visualisation for accurate and up-to-the-minute view of impending situations.  Make decisions based on facts – driven by insights, figure out what the data can and is trying to tell you.  Inform all of your people - to empower them to make the best decisions with the right information.
Consolidate and leverage data from multiple, disparate databases.
Perform self-service analytics,  which enables law enforcement departments to make faster decisions.
Terrorists, Rioters & Criminals co-ordinate and propagate their activities through social media.  We can move from a Reactive to a Proactive posture.
Use data to make proactive patrol decisions and prevent crime before it occurs.

Power BI, Power Map and Power Query are essential tools that could make a huge difference to the way you approach and apply insight from Big Data. Insight that already exists but simply cannot be accessed using traditional tools.

It enables you to look at the data you already have in new, exciting and empowering ways and is so important that it could literally mean the difference between life and death in a range of situations.
